    <statement>
        <p>
            A signal is sent down a fiber optic cable. Its strength decreases by 2% each mile it travels. (Say it was one unit strong to start.)
        </p>
        <ol marker="(a)">
            <li>
                <p>
                    Name the variables in this story.
                    <xi:include href="../name-variables.ptx" />
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    How strong is the signal after one mile?
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    How strong is the signal after two miles? (Hint: the answer is not 0.96.)
                </p>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </statement>
</activity>